{"tid":112840,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[讀報考古] 星島S-File","createTime":"2017-02-08T12:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T14:53:58.000Z","uid":83444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af14e8cd3b9633d922675653529d592d8bd183ee","tid":112840,"uid":83444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T12:55:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的，話說中學時代，某校曾經強逼全校學生訂報。而結果就係地球死多左好多棵樹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，同埋令我養成閱報儲報的習慣。自己想像下入面全部係明報副刊，仲有星島S-File。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i/lKAaM0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FlKAaM0.jpg&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8sVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=a1b1e067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://upload.cc/i/lKAaM0.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i/o9gXjZ.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fo9gXjZ.jpg&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8sVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=6d7a0b68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://upload.cc/i/o9gXjZ.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n鑒於香港土地問題，再加上儲舊報紙好似好無謂，但係就咁掉左佢又好似好曬。我決定每日剪少少上黎，當係懷舊又好、考古又好。<br />\n<br />\n第一箱開既係星島既S-File。"},{"pid":"5b6179d4ae8d46d7622815eb9c45681a518424b9","tid":112840,"uid":83444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T12:58:25.000Z","msg":"2007/10/02<br />\n<br />\n遺憾地哩日無咩特別<br />\n<br />\n封面<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/mG206g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FmG206g.jpg&h=dbc30fdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目錄<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/K8JorS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FK8JorS.jpg&h=1081e48f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯一特別少少係篇檸檬茶，令我諗起蕭源成日吹奏自己<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/kxWTJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FkxWTJb.jpg&h=ba63d9a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23f7f4b8694783d55e2b1ff1d6b08d80fa04b938","tid":112840,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T14:53:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}